    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/7a0b9643fb3577120b9b4c76c7272b46.avif?t=1750117714\" width=700 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/ab88a1cb14d924bc646c316605dbc055.poster.avif?t=1750117714\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/ab88a1cb14d924bc646c316605dbc055.webm?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/ab88a1cb14d924bc646c316605dbc055.mp4?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >放松身心，融入《Re:Fresh》的写意天地，享受来自一个光能朋克世界的怡人微风。这是一款 3D 探索平台收集马拉松游戏，你需要收集材料，帮助修复暴风雨后的小镇！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >预计游玩时间：1.5小时。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/61b34d9188a0e42925c6a856f1e341d0.avif?t=1750117714\" width=700 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/034dd5ecdf3dd61ec4761e7f6030e3d8.poster.avif?t=1750117714\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/034dd5ecdf3dd61ec4761e7f6030e3d8.webm?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/034dd5ecdf3dd61ec4761e7f6030e3d8.mp4?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由探索，随意掌控在这个开放世界的冒险节奏，收集光电池来升级你的行动选项。光电池是你跳跃和冲刺的主要能量来源，因此一定要检查每个角落，找到所有光电池。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/f28daa4d9978b18a52d7f82fe28f662c.avif?t=1750117714\" width=700 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/390a7eca959f23506a2a104788c2d4f2.poster.avif?t=1750117714\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/390a7eca959f23506a2a104788c2d4f2.webm?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/390a7eca959f23506a2a104788c2d4f2.mp4?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结交好友，与当地镇民交融互动，逐步了解你的社区！这里有一群可爱又呆萌的角色等着你去发现，每个角色都有独特的对话和花絮信息，他们迫不及待地想要和你分享。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/354d85c7c6033906925cf91e1ac473b2.poster.avif?t=1750117714\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/354d85c7c6033906925cf91e1ac473b2.webm?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/354d85c7c6033906925cf91e1ac473b2.mp4?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
